Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.93,0:22:17.66,mianze,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fade(500,500)}翻译:お兄さま&Sakura酱  校对:初夏  时间轴:河马君  后期:火猫少女  MKV:小圣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.38,0:00:12.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经没事了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.31,0:00:14.25,*Default,,0,0,0,,要问为什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.86,0:00:20.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我来了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.86,0:00:31.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超帅气 如果我拥有「个性」的话
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.58,0:00:33.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也好想变成这样
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.08,0:00:36.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还是放弃比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.50,0:00:42.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使事实是那样
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.10,0:00:46.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你别说是「弱小个性」根本就是「无个性」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.88,0:00:49.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你凭什么跟我站到同一个赛场
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.70,0:00:53.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你倒是说说你能做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.44,0:00:57.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪怕所有人都这样认为
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.64,0:00:59.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起 出久
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.56,0:01:02.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.94,0:01:07.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.72,0:01:09.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是这句话 妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.72,0:01:14.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使事实是那样 我也…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.78,0:01:16.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也还是会…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.24,0:01:21.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请问没有「个性」也能成为英雄吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.98,0:01:26.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请问没有「个性」的人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.00,0:01:29.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也能成为像你一样的人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.96,0:01:42.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「个性」…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.18,0:01:57.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 真的来不及了 可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.20,0:01:59.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我没有「个性」…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.44,0:02:03.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或许还有其他原因
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.62,0:02:05.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我一直遭人嘲笑
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.52,0:02:08.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以…虽然我也不太清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.58,0:02:13.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过我觉得救助他人是件很帅气的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.90,0:02:17.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且还带着无所畏惧的笑容去救助他人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.56,0:02:22.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也想成为像你这样最强的英雄…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.96,0:04:15.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.08,0:04:17.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底发生了什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.02,0:04:22.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「得克萨斯扣杀」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.02,0:04:22.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(424,437)\fs21}Texas Smash
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.60,0:04:22.28,Comment,NTP,0,0,0,,想起来了 都怪那个混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.80,0:04:27.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是没有那个混蛋的话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.96,0:04:31.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,胜己 你不是和绿谷一起长大的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.04,0:04:34.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你今天做的实在太过火了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.26,0:04:37.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都怪他想站在我想前进的道路上
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.54,0:04:40.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别这么暴躁了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.38,0:04:46.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是这是我小时候的目标
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.34,0:04:48.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且 那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.24,0:04:50.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不试试看的话 还不知道结果如何
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.62,0:04:55.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直像个傻瓜那样做着白日梦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.48,0:04:59.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看着就让人来气
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.46,0:05:03.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么就去游戏中心转换一下心情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.06,0:05:05.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,胜己也会来的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.65,0:05:07.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.66,0:05:09.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我们就去车站前的那家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.46,0:05:10.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毕竟那里的肥羊比较多
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.78,0:05:12.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也真够坏的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.02,0:05:16.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是被人发现了 可是会影响我的升学评价
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.82,0:05:18.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个!?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.66,0:05:24.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拥有优秀「个性」的隐身蓑衣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.07,0:05:29.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\b1\fn方正粗圆_GBK\pos(424,350)\fs41\bord2\xshad-5\alpha&H00&\1c&HFFFFFF&\4c&H000000&}第2话 {\r\b1\fn方正粗圆_GBK\pos(424,350)\fs41\bord2\xshad-5\alpha&H00&\1c&H1600CB&\4c&H000000&}英雄的条件
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.41,0:05:38.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么泄气了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.50,0:05:41.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明刚才还是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.58,0:05:44.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道是冒牌的!?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.62,0:05:45.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好瘦!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.60,0:05:49.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就是欧尔麦特
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.38,0:05:53.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,骗人!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.66,0:05:57.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在泳池不是经常看到有人持续收紧腹肌的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.46,0:05:58.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就那原理
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.26,0:06:01.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你骗我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.44,0:06:04.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你骗我…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.34,0:06:07.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欧尔麦特是带着无所畏惧的笑容…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.28,0:06:11.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,经常救助他人的最强…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.78,0:06:15.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无所畏惧的笑容吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.24,0:06:21.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少年 既然被你看到了 就顺便告诉你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.80,0:06:24.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可千万别在网上散播
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.84,0:06:31.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我五年前遭到敌人袭击所受的伤
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.02,0:06:36.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呼吸器官有一半损坏 而且连胃也要全部摘除
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.04,0:06:40.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为连番的手术以及后遗症 才让我憔悴成这样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.78,0:06:45.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我现在能变成英雄的可活动时间是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.54,0:06:48.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一天大概只有3个小时
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.14,0:06:51.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.98,0:06:55.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,五年前…难道是和「毒之链锯」的激战吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.32,0:06:57.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道的真多
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.94,0:07:00.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 我可不是输给那个无赖的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.78,0:07:04.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这件事并没有让民众所知
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.66,0:07:08.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我主动拜托别人不要公开
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.98,0:07:13.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,带着笑容救助他人的「和平象征」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.72,0:07:17.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是绝对不能被邪恶的势力击溃的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.54,0:07:22.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我之所以会带着那种笑容 是为了掩饰作为英雄的重压
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.72,0:07:27.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以及源于自己内心的恐惧 而在自欺欺人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.02,0:07:33.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,职业英雄总是奋身拚搏
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.40,0:07:36.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使没有「个性」也想成为英雄…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.00,0:07:38.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然不是绝对不可能…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.92,0:07:40.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过我实在说不出口
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.88,0:07:49.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你憧憬于救助他人的话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.68,0:07:51.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也可以选择成为警察
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.98,0:07:54.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然经常会被嘲笑说是「敌人接收专员」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.98,0:07:54.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(514,437)\fs21}Villain
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.06,0:07:56.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过那也是份很了不起的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.38,0:08:02.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有梦想并不是件坏事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.80,0:08:08.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过少年你也必须要接受相应的现实
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.20,0:08:16.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 得赶紧把这个家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.98,0:08:34.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.48,0:08:43.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是「敌人」 现在是哪个英雄在现场
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.48,0:08:43.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(281,437)\fs21}Villain
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.86,0:08:48.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使没有「个性」也想成为英雄…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.60,0:08:50.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然不是绝对不可能…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.46,0:08:52.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过我实在说不出口
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.30,0:09:17.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是「敌人」
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.30,0:09:17.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(439,437)\fs21}Villain
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.80,0:09:26.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然拿小孩当人质
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.96,0:09:29.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真卑鄙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.28,0:09:37.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.14,0:09:38.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抓不住!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.28,0:09:43.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「死亡赤拳」
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.86,0:09:44.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.44,0:09:49.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不准你们靠近我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.36,0:10:00.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我怎么会给这种臭男人吞噬掉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.48,0:10:03.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.62,0:10:13.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害的力量 这次真是中大奖了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.14,0:10:16.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要拥有这种力量和「个性」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.46,0:10:18.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就能找那家伙报仇了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.78,0:10:21.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害 那家伙是谁?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.80,0:10:23.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该不会那家伙是「敌人」那边的大人物?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.80,0:10:23.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(431,437)\fs21}Villain
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.12,0:10:26.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来了 是新人英雄的「Mt.雷迪」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.12,0:10:29.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.14,0:10:33.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果没有两车道以上的空间 我就进不去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.18,0:10:40.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不擅长应付爆炎系的「个性」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.88,0:10:42.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天就让给其他人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.30,0:10:44.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那真是多谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.72,0:10:46.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我这边光是灭火就忙不过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.44,0:10:47.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,消防车还没来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.04,0:10:49.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在情况如何?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.72,0:10:51.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黏糊糊的完全抓不住
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.64,0:10:54.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且那个拥有好「个性」的孩子在奋力抵抗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.90,0:10:56.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜他所赐 「敌人」都变成爆炸中心了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.90,0:10:56.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(367,437)\fs21}Villain
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.38,0:10:58.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为这三种原因导致现在的局面很难应付
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.92,0:11:04.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.22,0:11:09.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 现场的我们没有一个能应付
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.92,0:11:12.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只能等待其他拥有有利「个性」的英雄来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.20,0:11:15.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那之前我们把损害减少到最低
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.42,0:11:18.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别担心 马上有其他英雄过来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.44,0:11:22.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然很对不起那个孩子 不过只能让他再忍受一阵子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.74,0:11:24.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.77,0:11:27.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是我拥有把那家伙吹飞的力量就好了…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.06,0:11:31.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 感觉情况有些不妙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.38,0:11:32.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,英雄 加油
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.20,0:11:41.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是那个时候
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.72,0:11:45.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当时一心只顾着可活动时间
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.01,0:11:48.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明还教育了粉丝 自己竟然犯了这么严重的错误
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.44,0:11:50.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太没用了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.00,0:11:54.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,实在太没用了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.78,0:12:15.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都已经初三了 那家伙还没有认清现实
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.80,0:12:19.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在是大家需要为将来认真考虑的时期
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.70,0:12:22.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也必须要接受相应的现实
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.03,0:12:28.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,顶级的职业英雄都这么说了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.14,0:12:33.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要哭 你其实也知道现实吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.08,0:12:37.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明是知道 但还一直在极力挣扎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.28,0:12:40.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,假装看不见 暗示自己无视现实
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.59,0:12:48.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是刚才传出爆炸声的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.96,0:12:53.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂 出于习惯又绕到这里来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.96,0:12:59.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在还是别过去了 只会徒增伤感
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.72,0:13:02.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他为什么会在这里!?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.36,0:13:06.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道是欧尔麦特让他逃走了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.32,0:13:11.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中途掉了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.70,0:13:13.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果是那样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.56,0:13:17.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都是我的错
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.60,0:13:20.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么英雄都不战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.70,0:13:24.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没办法出手 有一名初中学生被抓来当人质
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.66,0:13:25.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从刚才开始一直都是那样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.84,0:13:27.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被抓来当人质…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.48,0:13:29.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从刚才开始一直都…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.70,0:13:32.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么痛苦还一直都在忍受吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.66,0:13:36.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那时我只是被挟持了几秒就觉得快死掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.30,0:13:39.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.68,0:13:43.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说那个「敌人」就是刚才欧尔麦特追的那家伙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.68,0:13:43.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(270,437)\fs21}Villain
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.30,0:13:45.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欧尔麦特!?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.34,0:13:46.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会吧 难道他来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.52,0:13:49.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像不久之前我还看到了他
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.34,0:13:50.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.80,0:13:52.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那欧尔麦特现在在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.94,0:14:01.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都是我的错
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.86,0:14:03.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他现在无法行动
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.12,0:14:06.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太没用了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.72,0:14:09.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,普通的方法是抓不住那家伙的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.10,0:14:13.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只能等待其他拥有有利「个性」的英雄来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.92,0:14:16.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,实在太没用了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.10,0:14:17.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加油
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.58,0:14:21.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.88,0:14:23.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我实在是太没用了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.78,0:14:26.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,救援很快就会来的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.00,0:14:28.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我真是太没用了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.22,0:14:32.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有哪位英雄很快就会…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.28,0:14:58.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋 站住 别过去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.18,0:15:00.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个小鬼…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.08,0:15:01.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,废久?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.82,0:15:03.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么我跑了出来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.10,0:15:05.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.68,0:15:06.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.56,0:15:09.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我炸死你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.46,0:15:11.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么办 怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.36,0:15:13.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个时候要…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.83,0:15:16.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs21\pos(160,212)\frz16\fsp15\1c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&\bord0}先发制人漆树锁牢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.83,0:15:16.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs21\pos(160,332)\frz17\fsp15\1c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&\bord0}在对手面前迅速地使用手臂（蔓藤）伸展 趁机将其拘束
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.83,0:15:16.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs21\pos(310,352)\frz19\fsp10\1c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&\bord0}优点:如果成功可以立刻封锁它的行动 \N同时对一点进行集中攻击 不受地点限制
